1
00:00:20,180 --> 00:00:26,020
=Manbo Destiny=

2
00:00:26,020 --> 00:00:27,980
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:35,400 --> 00:00:37,208
Take a break. Have some tea.

4
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:38,631
Thank you.

5
00:00:42,592 --> 00:00:44,400
Ever since I became the Regent,

6
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:46,592
state affairs have poured in
like a flood,

7
00:00:47,100 --> 00:00:49,000
pressing down on me
until I can hardly breathe.

8
00:00:50,208 --> 00:00:51,900
I used to think this was an honor,

9
00:00:52,938 --> 00:00:54,092
but now it seems

10
00:00:54,592 --> 00:00:55,862
it's nothing more than shackles.

11
00:00:57,169 --> 00:00:58,554
I'm no different.

12
00:00:58,900 --> 00:01:01,400
My father used to teach me every day,

13
00:01:01,631 --> 00:01:03,285
telling me I must become Queen.

14
00:01:03,708 --> 00:01:07,438
But now I realize that's not
what I want.

15
00:01:08,131 --> 00:01:11,131
I seem to be nothing more
than a sacrifice for my family.

16
00:01:14,285 --> 00:01:16,190
If we could leave this whirlpool
of power behind

17
00:01:16,208 --> 00:01:17,323
and live in the mountains,

18
00:01:17,823 --> 00:01:18,938
how free that would be.

19
00:01:21,900 --> 00:01:25,323
Lin Ge, if you're really willing
to let all this go,

20
00:01:25,592 --> 00:01:26,862
I'll stay by your side.

21
00:01:27,938 --> 00:01:31,938
I actually miss those days in Yunnan.

22
00:01:32,977 --> 00:01:33,823
Me too.

23
00:01:58,977 --> 00:02:00,515
That's a wrap.

24
00:02:12,522 --> 00:02:13,868
One cup of "love" milk tea.

25
00:02:15,700 --> 00:02:16,368
And this as well.

26
00:02:17,522 --> 00:02:19,176
This is your favorite flavor.

27
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:22,180
Want me to light it for you now?

28
00:02:23,637 --> 00:02:24,445
You bought this?

29
00:02:25,753 --> 00:02:26,214
I did.

30
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:28,869
I remember

31
00:02:29,754 --> 00:02:31,869
weren't you kind of stingy?

32
00:02:31,869 --> 00:02:33,831
Where did you get the money
for all this?

33
00:02:37,254 --> 00:02:38,638
Did you steal it from someone?

34
00:02:38,638 --> 00:02:40,100
Hey, stop! That hurts!

35
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:41,620
Stop.

36
00:02:41,908 --> 00:02:43,831
No way, how could I?

37
00:02:44,523 --> 00:02:46,523
You're my boss now.

38
00:02:46,523 --> 00:02:48,600
I want to take good care of you.

39
00:02:51,408 --> 00:02:52,061
Right.

40
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:57,523
See? All these snacks you like,

41
00:02:57,792 --> 00:02:59,100
and your favorite face masks.

42
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,600
Everything you need.

43
00:03:01,792 --> 00:03:02,292
So?

44
00:03:05,292 --> 00:03:06,831
You're sure you bought all this?

45
00:03:07,177 --> 00:03:08,638
Absolutely.

46
00:03:09,061 --> 00:03:09,715
Do you remember?

47
00:03:10,138 --> 00:03:11,638
Back when we were dating...

48
00:03:15,138 --> 00:03:16,792
Besides these,

49
00:03:16,792 --> 00:03:17,677
what else do you want?

50
00:03:18,215 --> 00:03:18,908
I'll go buy it.

51
00:03:21,177 --> 00:03:22,100
I want tamarind.

52
00:03:22,523 --> 00:03:23,523
Tamarind?

53
00:03:24,254 --> 00:03:26,638
Got it. Wait here.

54
00:03:33,369 --> 00:03:36,138
(Zhong Cheng wouldn't know
I like this flavor.)

55
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:37,831
(It must be him.)

56
00:03:44,446 --> 00:03:45,023
Mengmeng.

57
00:03:45,908 --> 00:03:46,600
Look.

58
00:03:47,331 --> 00:03:48,177
I bought it for you.

59
00:03:53,908 --> 00:03:55,446
Your favorite tamarind.

60
00:04:03,023 --> 00:04:04,831
Mengmeng, what's wrong?

61
00:04:05,369 --> 00:04:06,331
Did I get the wrong one?

62
00:04:07,292 --> 00:04:07,985
It's nothing.

63
00:04:09,138 --> 00:04:10,446
I don't feel like driving anymore.

64
00:04:10,677 --> 00:04:12,023
Help me call a ride later.

65
00:04:12,908 --> 00:04:13,792
Why are you crying?

66
00:04:18,677 --> 00:04:19,138
Alright.

67
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:20,369
I'll get going first.

68
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,369
Remember to eat it.

69
00:04:24,561 --> 00:04:25,215
I bought a lot.

70
00:04:25,715 --> 00:04:26,523
Don't forget to eat.

71
00:04:27,561 --> 00:04:28,331
I'm leaving then.

72
00:04:44,023 --> 00:04:46,100
I know everything today was done by you.

73
00:04:48,523 --> 00:04:49,869
This is the last time.

74
00:04:51,408 --> 00:04:52,523
From now on,

75
00:04:54,177 --> 00:04:55,715
don't come looking for me again.

76
00:04:56,985 --> 00:04:58,561
I really don't want to see you anymore.

77
00:05:02,061 --> 00:05:02,831
(Song Pai.)

78
00:05:03,100 --> 00:05:05,100
(Maybe our story has reached its end.)

79
00:05:05,446 --> 00:05:07,023
(Every moment I spent with you)

80
00:05:07,061 --> 00:05:08,600
(is my most precious memory.)

81
00:05:09,061 --> 00:05:10,177
(But to protect you,)

82
00:05:10,561 --> 00:05:11,985
(I can only let go of your hand.)

83
00:05:12,561 --> 00:05:15,831
(I'll pray for you quietly
from somewhere far away.)

84
00:05:15,831 --> 00:05:18,100
(Amid this turbulent palace struggle,)

85
00:05:18,254 --> 00:05:19,908
(I hope you stay safe.)

86
00:05:19,908 --> 00:05:21,138
(May your wishes come true.)

87
00:05:21,138 --> 00:05:22,792
(I also hope you overcome
every obstacle,)

88
00:05:23,446 --> 00:05:26,254
(and lead the people of this land
to prosperity.)

89
00:05:26,254 --> 00:05:28,677
(I hope you can achieve your dreams.)

90
00:05:32,408 --> 00:05:35,601
(Mengmeng, although I don't know
why you pushed me away,)

91
00:05:35,716 --> 00:05:37,216
(you must have your reasons.)

92
00:05:37,408 --> 00:05:39,255
(I will make you tell me in person.)

93
00:05:39,370 --> 00:05:40,870
(I will not give up.)

94
00:05:51,178 --> 00:05:53,062
Lin Ge, why are you here?

95
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,390
You didn't go back all night.

96
00:05:54,562 --> 00:05:55,831
I was thinking.

97
00:05:58,947 --> 00:05:59,831
What's wrong?

98
00:06:01,524 --> 00:06:02,947
I finally understand now.

99
00:06:04,101 --> 00:06:06,524
All my mother ever pursued was power.

100
00:06:07,678 --> 00:06:08,447
And I...

101
00:06:09,485 --> 00:06:10,524
All this time,

102
00:06:11,178 --> 00:06:12,408
I only wanted her approval.

103
00:06:14,062 --> 00:06:15,178
Actually,

104
00:06:15,793 --> 00:06:17,331
Song Pai is also quite pitiful.

105
00:06:18,062 --> 00:06:19,485
He has sacrificed too much.

106
00:06:20,870 --> 00:06:22,024
Even Mengmeng too.

107
00:06:24,947 --> 00:06:26,139
If it weren't for her,

108
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:27,790
my brother probably would have...

109
00:06:31,562 --> 00:06:34,178
The mastermind behind all this

110
00:06:34,947 --> 00:06:36,101
turns out to be my mother.

111
00:06:37,908 --> 00:06:38,485
You tell me,

112
00:06:41,255 --> 00:06:42,716
how should I face my brother?

113
00:06:44,447 --> 00:06:45,760
You don't need to blame yourself.

114
00:06:47,716 --> 00:06:50,485
There are things
I didn't dare to tell you.

115
00:06:52,139 --> 00:06:55,370
That night, Song Pai went
to my house to steal a contract.

116
00:06:55,831 --> 00:06:56,908
What contract?

117
00:06:57,408 --> 00:06:59,139
I also found out by accident.

118
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:02,601
Song Pai and Mengmeng
have a contract marriage.

119
00:07:06,062 --> 00:07:07,524
So I used it as a condition

120
00:07:08,101 --> 00:07:09,793
to make them cooperate with us.

121
00:07:11,601 --> 00:07:13,062
If we failed in the succession,

122
00:07:14,030 --> 00:07:15,370
it would still be our backup plan.

123
00:07:17,370 --> 00:07:18,678
I see.

124
00:07:19,331 --> 00:07:21,293
But I underestimated
my father's ambition.

125
00:07:22,101 --> 00:07:23,870
He secretly changed the contract

126
00:07:24,293 --> 00:07:26,447
and even threatened Song Pai
to quit the succession.

127
00:07:28,293 --> 00:07:31,447
If your father's ambition
isn't eliminated,

128
00:07:32,500 --> 00:07:34,562
he will eventually destroy
the entire royal family.

129
00:07:35,408 --> 00:07:37,831
Na, regarding your father...

130
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:42,169
Although I love my father,

131
00:07:42,939 --> 00:07:44,516
I love my country even more.

132
00:07:46,285 --> 00:07:48,092
Given the current situation,

133
00:07:48,208 --> 00:07:50,285
we must fully support Song Pai.

134
00:07:53,669 --> 00:07:55,554
I will do my best
to turn this situation around,

135
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,690
even if it means breaking
with my mother.

136
00:07:58,785 --> 00:08:01,054
I will make sure my brother,
Guan Mengmeng,

137
00:08:01,592 --> 00:08:02,285
and you

138
00:08:03,169 --> 00:08:04,439
receive the fairest treatment.

139
00:08:15,125 --> 00:08:17,086
What? You don't want to be the king?

140
00:08:17,317 --> 00:08:18,663
Did Song Pai force you?

141
00:08:19,163 --> 00:08:20,125
Not him.

142
00:08:21,202 --> 00:08:22,048
It's my own choice.

143
00:08:22,702 --> 00:08:24,317
Since I got involved in state affairs,

144
00:08:24,509 --> 00:08:27,009
I realized I'm not suitable
to be the heir.

145
00:08:30,009 --> 00:08:32,202
No one is more suitable than you.

146
00:08:32,410 --> 00:08:34,260
Song Pai has already given up
the succession.

147
00:08:34,471 --> 00:08:35,702
You are now the only heir.

148
00:08:36,048 --> 00:08:37,625
You can't give up at this moment.

149
00:08:41,625 --> 00:08:42,932
Nana and I have made up our minds.

150
00:08:43,971 --> 00:08:45,202
I don't want to be the king.

151
00:08:45,202 --> 00:08:46,320
She doesn't want to be queen.

152
00:08:46,790 --> 00:08:48,163
We just want to live a normal life.

153
00:08:48,625 --> 00:08:50,125
Yes, Your Highness.

154
00:08:50,317 --> 00:08:52,125
Lin Ge and I have decided

155
00:08:52,471 --> 00:08:54,048
to live a normal life.

156
00:08:56,548 --> 00:08:58,817
Did you put some kind
of spell on Lin Ge?

157
00:09:02,125 --> 00:09:02,740
Mother,

158
00:09:03,971 --> 00:09:05,009
I don't want it myself.

159
00:09:05,471 --> 00:09:06,702
It has nothing to do with Nana.

160
00:09:07,432 --> 00:09:08,202
Also,

161
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,509
if I become the king,

162
00:09:10,779 --> 00:09:12,279
my whole life will be trapped.

163
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,817
Do you want to see me unhappy forever?

164
00:09:15,894 --> 00:09:19,125
Besides, my brother is naturally
more suited to be the heir.

165
00:09:21,894 --> 00:09:22,509
Lin Ge,

166
00:09:23,548 --> 00:09:24,625
you are still young.

167
00:09:25,394 --> 00:09:27,317
You cannot understand my intention.

168
00:09:28,586 --> 00:09:29,394
It's okay.

169
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,279
I understand you.

170
00:09:32,509 --> 00:09:34,894
No mother does not love her child.

171
00:09:35,894 --> 00:09:37,625
If you cannot be heir,

172
00:09:39,048 --> 00:09:41,317
I will never rest in peace.

173
00:09:47,432 --> 00:09:47,894
Lin Ge.

174
00:09:48,663 --> 00:09:49,202
Lin Ge.

175
00:09:55,471 --> 00:09:58,086
Song Pai, if I'm not mistaken,

176
00:09:58,663 --> 00:10:00,317
tomorrow is your birthday.

177
00:10:00,817 --> 00:10:01,779
Then I will make your

178
00:10:02,548 --> 00:10:05,048
birthday a day of sacrifice.

179
00:10:05,779 --> 00:10:06,548
Mother,

180
00:10:08,009 --> 00:10:09,356
don't keep making mistakes.

181
00:10:10,471 --> 00:10:11,509
Stop it.

182
00:10:21,681 --> 00:10:22,873
Baofan.

183
00:10:23,373 --> 00:10:24,142
Yes.

184
00:10:25,027 --> 00:10:26,219
When will Lin Ge arrive?

185
00:10:27,527 --> 00:10:30,566
It's strange. I remember
the Second Prince isn't one to be late.

186
00:10:30,566 --> 00:10:31,796
It's been half an hour.

187
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:40,239
(First Princess,
today is the First Prince's birthday.)

188
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,374
(The Second Prince invited him to
celebrate at the poolside restaurant.)

189
00:10:41,375 --> 00:10:42,316
(Although the First Prince
didn't say it,)

190
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,380
(I know he must really want to see you.
He hopes you'll come.)

191
00:10:43,700 --> 00:10:44,739
No matter what,

192
00:10:45,085 --> 00:10:45,931
Song Pai,

193
00:10:47,085 --> 00:10:48,970
let me spend
your last birthday with you.

194
00:11:09,577 --> 00:11:10,885
Did Lin Ge arrange this?

195
00:11:10,885 --> 00:11:11,500
Maybe.

196
00:11:37,039 --> 00:11:37,654
Dance!

197
00:12:03,728 --> 00:12:04,300
I'll help you.

198
00:12:09,228 --> 00:12:10,805
Boss, he wants you to make a wish.

199
00:12:12,344 --> 00:12:12,767
Okay.

200
00:12:17,151 --> 00:12:18,690
I hope she comes back to find me.

201
00:12:23,344 --> 00:12:24,344
Thank you.

202
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,536
You were sent here by Lin Ge, right?

203
00:12:31,805 --> 00:12:32,805
Thanks for today.

204
00:12:34,190 --> 00:12:36,959
My wish probably
cannot come true for now.

205
00:12:37,805 --> 00:12:38,613
But it's okay.

206
00:12:39,100 --> 00:12:40,344
I can make your wish come true.

207
00:12:41,382 --> 00:12:42,497
Take off your hood.

208
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:49,031
What's wrong?
Is it because your store manager

209
00:12:49,055 --> 00:12:50,613
doesn't allow you to take off your hood,

210
00:12:50,613 --> 00:12:51,805
so you're afraid?

211
00:12:53,190 --> 00:12:54,574
It's fine, take it off.

212
00:12:58,690 --> 00:13:01,113
You've already successfully
caught my attention.

213
00:13:01,767 --> 00:13:02,344
Come on.

214
00:13:03,497 --> 00:13:05,344
Say the wish you want to fulfill.

215
00:13:05,920 --> 00:13:06,536
Take it off.

216
00:13:16,613 --> 00:13:17,728
Take off the hood.

217
00:13:36,086 --> 00:13:36,740
Nana!

218
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:37,547
Nana!

219
00:13:40,701 --> 00:13:41,355
Lin Ge.

220
00:13:47,201 --> 00:13:48,086
Something's wrong.

221
00:13:49,009 --> 00:13:50,278
The First Prince is in danger!

222
00:13:50,778 --> 00:13:51,470
My brother?

223
00:13:56,509 --> 00:13:57,201
Open the door!

224
00:13:57,970 --> 00:13:58,778
Open the door!

225
00:14:02,278 --> 00:14:03,317
Someone help!

226
00:14:03,509 --> 00:14:04,278
Someone help!

227
00:14:04,278 --> 00:14:06,047
Second Prince has fainted!

228
00:14:09,163 --> 00:14:10,278
Quick, check on him!

229
00:14:19,509 --> 00:14:20,509
You scared me to death.

230
00:14:21,432 --> 00:14:22,086
Hurry, go!

231
00:14:22,432 --> 00:14:23,701
Hope my brother is okay.

232
00:14:33,020 --> 00:14:35,500
♪I do this for you♪

233
00:14:35,900 --> 00:14:38,140
♪The love is fake♪

234
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:40,900
♪The love is true♪

235
00:14:41,700 --> 00:14:43,780
♪For you♪
